          {
            "nodeType": "paragraph",
            "data": {},
            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Place a marker in a space up to 3 spaces away and choose one of the below effects. If any creature moves into or out of the space with the marker or an adjacent space, make a skill vs. agility roll and remove the marker. If the attack hits, apply the chosen effect. You may use this ability outside of combat without counting the heroic action as being used.",
